@publisher_token = init
@rider_token = init
@order_id = 0

### ========== 用户认证 ==========

### ##0 发单人登录 (模拟微信登录，获取token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "publisher001"
}

> {%
    // 关键点：去运行窗口看一下，Rikki 返回的到底是 data 还是 token？
    // 如果返回 {"code":200, "data":"eyJ..."}，这里就写 response.body.data
    client.global.set("publisher_token", response.body.data);
%}

### ##0.1 骑手登录 (模拟微信登录，获取token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "rider001"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("rider_token", response.body.token);
%}

### ========== 完整链路测试 ==========
### 先依次执行上面两个登录，token 会自动保存到变量中

### ##1 AI 智能发单 (用发单人token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/ai-publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{publisher_token}}

{
  "text": "帮我从菜鸟驿站A12取个快递，送到6栋512，手机号13800138000，跑腿费5块"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("order_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### ##2 查看跑腿大厅 (任意已登录用户)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/list/hall
Authorization: Bearer {{rider_token}}

### ##3 骑手抢单 (status: 0 -> 1 待取货)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/accept?orderId={{order_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{rider_token}}

### ##4 骑手取件 (status: 1 -> 2 配送中)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/take
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{rider_token}}

{
  "orderId": "{{order_id}}",
  "pickupPhotoUrl": "https://img.relay.com/pickup/20250101_001.jpg"
}

### ##5 骑手确认送达 (status: 2 -> 3 待确认)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/deliver
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{rider_token}}

{
  "orderId": "{{order_id}}",
  "deliveryPhotoUrl": "https://img.relay.com/deliver/20250101_001.jpg"
}

### ##6 用户确认收货 (status: 3 -> 4 已完成)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/confirm?orderId={{order_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{publisher_token}}

